    <h2><strong>What is my skin type?</strong></h2>
    <p>We get it — today’s beauty market is overwhelming. The sheer volume of products and information can feel daunting, and choosing the right, personalized products for your individual skin has never seemed more difficult.</p>
    <p>Whether you have an oily skin type, sensitive skin type, or normal skin, knowing what type of skin you have is the first step to finding your bespoke routine and achieving that dewy, glowy, and healthy skin complexion you've always dreamed of. Everyone's skin is as unique as they are, and understanding your skin type is vital in unlocking its radiance potential. It's like matching on a dating app—once you know what you're looking for, you can easily swipe left on the skincare products that don't click, and swipe right on the ones you know your skin will love. We're here to help you decode your skin's love language to curate the perfect routine for a skincare match made in heaven.</p>
</div>

