<div class="article__section-container">
    <h3 style="padding-top:20px;"><strong>Normal Skin Type:</strong></h3>
    <p>The Goldilocks skin type. Not too oily, not too dry, but just right. Characterized by even moisture levels and few imperfections, normal skin is well-balanced, with small pores, a smooth texture, and minimal sensitivity to products. Since you’ve lucked out with natural harmony, normal skin doesn’t need intense products; opt for gentle, regular cleansing, lightweight moisturizing, and sun protection that provides hydration without overwhelming the skin.</p>
    <p><strong>Recommended products:</strong> Lucky you! Our collections are made for all skin types, and with your balanced normal skin, any of our skincare collections will gently cleanse, nourish, and boost your glow to its maximum dewy potential. Try a couple depending on your personalized skin goals to find your favorites!</p>

    <h3 style="padding-top:20px;"><strong>Dry Skin Type:</strong></h3>
    <p>Drink up! Dry skin often feels tight, rough, and desperate for moisture. It's prone to redness, irritation, and flakiness, often appearing dull due to dehydration. Intense moisture is key for dry skin types, so look for rich creams, nourishing serums, gentle cleansers, and hydrating sunscreens. Read our recommended dry skincare routine <a href="https://www.pacificabeauty.com/blogs/the-compassionista/the-ideal-skincare-routine-for-dry-skin">here</a>.</p>
    <p><strong>Recommended products:</strong> Formulated with skinfirst, biocompatible ingredients, Pacifica Beauty’s <a href="https://www.pacificabeauty.com/collections/future-youth">Future Youth</a> and <a href="https://www.pacificabeauty.com/collections/vegan-collagen">Vegan Collagen</a> collections contain our most hydrating, nourishing products backed by science and clinical studies.</p>
</div>

