<div class="article__section-container">
    <h3 style="padding-top:20px;"><strong>Combination Skin Type:</strong></h3>
    <p>This skin’s got a little bit of everything. Characterized by oiliness in certain areas (especially the T-zone) and dryness in others, combination skin can look like recurrent breakouts in oily zones alongside parched areas that look rough or dull. Although balancing hydration while targeting excess sebum sounds like a challenging type to figure out, strike a balance with gentle cleansers, targeted treatments for specific breakout areas, nourishing yet lightweight moisturizers, and non-comedogenic sun protection. Balance is key.</p>
    <p><strong>Recommended products:</strong> Thoroughly cleanse and target excessive sebum areas with Pacifica Beauty’s <a href="https://www.pacificabeauty.com/collections/kale-skincare">Kale Detox</a> products, help fade hyperpigmentation from breakout zones with <a href="https://www.pacificabeauty.com/collections/glow-baby">Glow Baby</a>, while hydrating and repairing your skin with <a href="https://www.pacificabeauty.com/collections/wake-up-beautiful">Wake Up Beautiful</a> retinoid serums and creams. All our skincare collections are formulated for all skin types, so try a couple to find products that suit your preference.</p>

    <h3 style="padding-top:20px;"><strong>Sensitive Skin Type:</strong></h3>
    <p>Handle with care. Sensitive skin can be easily irritated by external and environmental factors like weather, strong fragrances, and harsh ingredients. It may appear red, inflamed, or itchy, and requires extra tender loving care. Opt for fragrance-free, hypoallergenic, and dermatologist-approved products formulated with soothing natural ingredients aimed at hydration and reducing skinflammation. Read our recommended sensitive skincare routine <a href="https://www.pacificabeauty.com/blogs/the-compassionista/a-gentle-skincare-routine-for-sensitive-skin">here</a>.</p>
    <p><strong>Recommended products:</strong> Fragrance-free, dermatologist + allergy tested, and accepted by the National Eczema Association, our <a href="https://www.pacificabeauty.com/collections/vegan-ceramide">Vegan Ceramide</a> collection is sensitive skin’s most loyal bestie. Restoring the skin’s protective barrier function, these products deeply nourish, soothe, and balance for calm and happy skin.</p>
</div>

